        "template--17062096503099__15d37dcd-dfe5-404c-80f1-8f76c2017e23-16696259764c4b7b62-0": {
          "type": "topic",
          "settings": {
            "is_open": true,
            "title": "Do your products actually work?",
            "text": "<p>We didn’t spend two years hunting down the best mushrooms on the planet for a placebo. Each one is packed with bioactive compounds that support energy, focus, stress, gut health and skin. You’ll feel it.</p><p>If you don’t, you’re covered by our 30 day money back guarantee.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "template--17062096503099__15d37dcd-dfe5-404c-80f1-8f76c2017e23-16696259764c4b7b62-1": {
          "type": "topic",
          "settings": {
            "is_open": false,
            "title": "What do they taste like?",
            "text": "<p>Not gonna lie, they taste like mushrooms. Earthy, a bit bold, not your vanilla latte.</p><p>If you’re fussy, mix it into coffee, smoothies or something sweet. If not, neck it and get on with your life.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "template--17062096503099__15d37dcd-dfe5-404c-80f1-8f76c2017e23-16696259764c4b7b62-2": {
          "type": "topic",
          "settings": {
            "is_open": false,
            "title": "How do I take Pure Filth mushrooms and what with?",
            "text": "<p>Chuck it in your coffee, smoothie or shake. Whatever you’re already having.</p><p>Hot or cold, doesn’t matter. Just get it in and crack on.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "topic_tbVqpp": {
          "type": "topic",
          "settings": {
            "is_open": false,
            "title": "Can I take them daily and can I stack them?",
            "text": "<p>Daily, baby. One serving is 2g. You can go up to 6g per day, so feel free to mix and match if you want to level things up. Or keep it simple.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "topic_ejc3cx": {
          "type": "topic",
          "settings": {
            "is_open": false,
            "title": "Are your mushrooms third party tested?",
            "text": "<p>Damn right. Every batch is tested for quality, potency, and purity. No fillers, no nasties, just the good stuff.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "topic_txPMFK": {
          "type": "topic",
          "settings": {
            "is_open": false,
            "title": "What’s the difference between fruiting body and mycelium?",
            "text": "<p>Fruiting body is where the bioactive compounds live. That’s the part you actually want.</p><p>Mycelium is the root like structure often grown on grains, which means more filler and less fungi. Not our vibe.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "topic_PUUHKt": {
          "type": "topic",
          "settings": {
            "is_open": false,
            "title": "How are your mushrooms made and is there alcohol in them?",
            "text": "<p>We use a dual extraction method using water and alcohol to pull out all the good stuff.</p><p>The final product contains zero alcohol. Just pure, potent mushroom powder.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "topic_4m4iX8": {
          "type": "topic",
          "settings": {
            "is_open": false,
            "title": "Are your mushrooms legal?",
            "text": "<p>Relax. These are functional mushrooms, not the psychedelic kind.</p><p>Think focus and calm, not seeing sounds.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
